     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "\n",
      "t test of coefficients:\n",
      "\n",
      "               Estimate  Std. Error t value  Pr(>|t|)    \n",
      "(Intercept)  1.4985e+01  3.2600e+00  4.5966  4.54e-06 ***\n",
      "demand       1.1765e-03  1.3493e-04  8.7191 < 2.2e-16 ***\n",
      "wind        -9.7955e-05  1.5284e-04 -0.6409   0.52166    \n",
      "solar       -5.3715e-05  5.2089e-04 -0.1031   0.91788    \n",
      "wind_lag1    2.9872e-04  1.5483e-04  1.9294   0.05382 .  \n",
      "solar_lag1  -1.1214e-04  5.3038e-04 -0.2114   0.83257    \n",
